              <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark text-sm">
                <p>Yes, Sotai can be very helpful for arthritis due to its gentleness. Use minimal effort, practice shorter and more frequent sessions, and some days you may need to practice very gently or skip entirely. Track which exercises help most and always stay within comfortable ranges.</p>
              </div>
