              <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark text-sm">
                <p>Many people notice immediate improvement in range of motion and pain reduction after a single session. For lasting changes, expect noticeable improvement within 1-2 weeks of daily practice, with significant results in 4-6 weeks. Complex or chronic issues may take longer.</p>
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group rounded-xl">
