                <span class="ml-4 flex-shrink-0 text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180">&#9660;</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark text-sm">
                <p>Sotai is designed for self-practice. All the exercises in this article can be done alone. However, working with a trained practitioner can accelerate your progress, especially for complex or severe issues. Consider professional guidance if self-practice isn't producing expected results.</p>
