              <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark text-sm">
                <p>If both directions feel equal, choose either one—your body may be relatively balanced in that area. If both feel uncomfortable, start with the one that feels slightly less uncomfortable and use even less effort (20-30%). Sometimes the difference is very subtle and becomes clearer with practice.</p>
